<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BEHOLD, WHAT LOVE!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaiun Pa hehpihna nasa,
 Ei piek tawpneilo chuh;
 Gilo mangthai &quot;Pathien cha a,&quot;
 Sim tel I hih theihna'n.

[V2]
 &quot;Ngai un, ei hehpihzie chuh,
 Pa'n eihaw ei hehpihzie chu a nasa nazen e;
 Pathien chate hi ding a,
 Sim tel a I um theihna'n!&quot;

[V3]
 2. Amah apat gamla talo,
 &quot;Thisan lun&quot; ziek' I naih;
 &quot;Deihtaka pawmin I um tau,&quot;
 Pathien lunggil sung ah.

[V4]
 3. Lopina bangti I chang dem,
 &quot;Tih a kilang nai puoi,&quot;
 Lalpa deihum I muh tiengleh,
 Amah mel bang pu'i tiu.

[V5]
 4. Zie bang kinepna chuh nei in,
 I thientho diu ahi;
 Chawmlo a I muh pai ding uh,
 Lalpa thokit bang in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>21</hymn_number>
</song>